 ↞---------------|ABILITIES|---------------↠

  Thick-fat:

    This Pokémon takes half as 
  much damage from fire- and ice-type 
  moves.

  Scrappy:

    This Pokémon ignores ghost-type 
  Pokémon's immunity to normal- 
  and fighting-type moves.

  Ghost Pokémon's other types 
  affect damage as usual.

  Sap-sipper:

    Whenever a grass-type move 
  hits this Pokémon, its Attack 
  rises one stage, negating any 
  other effect on it.


